metadata.name: The journey begins
metadata.description:
Here we are, Paris, France! 
What a busy place this is. Let's check Google Maps first.
Right across the street is Notre Dame. So sorry for the big fire that destroyed the entire roof back in 2019. Guess we should go and get a traditional Croissant before we start, right? Let's move on to photo 2/12.

Location: Paris, France
GMaps: https://goo.gl/maps/fFajyNggjsNDnJZ88
Date: April 2022
Resolution: 2870x4305
Shot by: @SirTificate_hh
